plot: Mikael Wulff and the fascist hippo Dolph head on a wildlife survival adventure in Kosovo. On their way they encounter the brother to Danish pop singer Anders Frandsen, and the following morning Wulff is nowhere in sight.
title: Dolph & Wulff på afveje
